show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Zhong Lin, in order to recover the unpaid wages of his coworkers, agrees to Mr. Jiang's condition to take the blame for his son, Jiang Yuan, who caused an accident while drunk. Five years later, after being released from prison, Zhong Lin discovers that his family has been persecuted and gone missing. To find his wife and daughter, he arrives in Picheng and starts working as a construction worker, using every moment he has to search for them. However, he soon faces new troubles, as various crises begin to emerge one after another.
